     C                     Z-ADDDAMKLT    WAMKLT  31
     C                     MOVELDACOLR    WACOLR  1
     C                     Z-ADDDASIZE    WASIZE  20
     C                     Z-ADDDAKUBI    WAKUBI  30
     C                     Z-ADDDACIHI    WACIHI  20
     C                     Z-ADDDACIBI    WACIBI  20
     C                     Z-ADDDACIOK    WACIOK  20
     C                     MOVELDAOFFL    WAOFFL  1
